plainText:
Dear All,

Hope you are doing well. I want to remind you that we have a mid-project update tomorrow (Wednesday, October 29). You will need to present your project progress as a group. Each group will have 12 minutes. You don’t need to spend too much time on fancy slides, instead present the progress you have made, what remains to be done, and your plan to complete the project by the deadline.

Feel free to reach out if you have any questions.

Thanks,
Raiful

Replies to this email will be posted as a reply to the announcement, which will be seen by everyone in the course.

[https://du11hjcvx0uqb.cloudfront.net/dist/images/email_signature-d2c5880612.png]
